Integrate[Erf[a_.+b_*x_]^2,x_] := (a+b*x)*Erf[a+b*x]^2/b - 4/Sqrt[Pi]*Integrate[(a+b*x)*Erf[a+b*x]/E^(a+b*x)^2,x] /;
